1
00:00:13,416 --> 00:00:18,666
So tell me... Why do
you wish to slay me?

2
00:00:18,750 --> 00:00:20,833
Because I am under
strict orders from someone

3
00:00:20,916 --> 00:00:23,958
who has deemed you
to be a nuisance.

4
00:00:24,041 --> 00:00:28,583
And yet... your will
plays no part in this?

5
00:00:28,666 --> 00:00:30,000
None.

6
00:02:37,875 --> 00:02:42,833
[CASSHERN SOBS]

7
00:03:05,250 --> 00:03:06,458
Here ya' go.

8
00:03:06,541 --> 00:03:10,916
[ROBOTS LAUGH]

9
00:03:11,000 --> 00:03:12,583
Pretty!

10
00:03:24,000 --> 00:03:29,083
[CASSHERN GRUNTS]

11
00:03:29,166 --> 00:03:31,208
[CASSHERN] Why?

12
00:03:31,291 --> 00:03:33,041
I wanna know!

13
00:03:33,125 --> 00:03:36,083
[PADDING]

14
00:03:43,875 --> 00:03:46,291
Hey Friender.

15
00:03:50,083 --> 00:03:54,833
[FRIENDER GROWLS]

16
00:04:19,666 --> 00:04:21,875
[LYUZE]
Are you crying?

17
00:04:28,750 --> 00:04:30,958
Like a human.

18
00:04:31,041 --> 00:04:33,666
It's you...

19
00:04:33,750 --> 00:04:35,333
[LYUZE]
It's said that humans shed tears

20
00:04:35,416 --> 00:04:37,333
whenever they are sad...

21
00:04:37,416 --> 00:04:39,541
What brings on your tears?

22
00:04:39,625 --> 00:04:43,000
What are you sad about?

23
00:04:43,083 --> 00:04:45,000
[CASSHERN] I...

24
00:04:45,083 --> 00:04:48,833
I destroyed the world...
with this hand.

25
00:04:50,083 --> 00:04:53,291
I see... your memory
must be coming back... 

26
00:04:53,375 --> 00:04:56,416
The past you hoped
you would forget forever...

27
00:04:56,500 --> 00:05:00,083
now you're filled with
regret and crying over it?

28
00:05:00,166 --> 00:05:02,250
Stop feeling
sorry for yourself!

29
00:05:02,333 --> 00:05:05,166
Why go through with it when
you knew you'd regret it later?

30
00:05:05,250 --> 00:05:06,791
[CASSHERN]
I don't know...

31
00:05:06,875 --> 00:05:10,625
I can't remember...
Not one thing.

32
00:05:10,708 --> 00:05:13,833
[LYUZE]
You just said with this hand.

33
00:05:13,916 --> 00:05:16,416
So you obviously
remember something.

34
00:05:16,500 --> 00:05:18,541
That's not the case...

35
00:05:18,625 --> 00:05:21,583
It's... everyone
telling me it's my fault.

36
00:05:23,416 --> 00:05:25,500
[LYUZE]
And they are right...

37
00:05:25,583 --> 00:05:28,500
You made the world
the way it is... 

38
00:05:28,583 --> 00:05:31,333
You killed Luna...

39
00:05:31,416 --> 00:05:34,375
The Sun that was called Moon!

40
00:05:34,458 --> 00:05:36,708
But why did I?

41
00:05:36,791 --> 00:05:39,375
What reason did
I have to kill her?

42
00:05:41,458 --> 00:05:45,916
You don't remember
anything...? Honestly?

43
00:05:46,000 --> 00:05:50,208
My past is
a void... I swear.

44
00:05:50,291 --> 00:05:52,083
I don't know why
I would do such a thing.

45
00:05:52,166 --> 00:05:54,750
You're a liar!

46
00:05:54,833 --> 00:05:56,291
Do you really expect
me to believe

47
00:05:56,375 --> 00:05:59,708
you can't remember committing
such a horrible crime?

48
00:06:01,666 --> 00:06:05,458
I am certain...
that I was at fault.

49
00:06:07,791 --> 00:06:08,958
Damn right...

50
00:06:09,041 --> 00:06:11,083
If you'd just refrained
from getting involved...

51
00:06:11,166 --> 00:06:13,208
...the entire world...

52
00:06:13,291 --> 00:06:15,208
My big sister...

53
00:06:15,291 --> 00:06:17,041
Your sister?

54
00:06:20,125 --> 00:06:24,500
Are you saying
I killed... your sister?

55
00:06:24,583 --> 00:06:28,083
[LYUZE]
Yes... She died by your hand.

56
00:06:30,708 --> 00:06:33,416
Since you seem to have
forgotten I'll just tell you.

57
00:06:33,500 --> 00:06:36,333
Every detail of what you did... 

58
00:06:36,416 --> 00:06:39,083
I'll show you...
what a miserable end

59
00:06:39,166 --> 00:06:42,583
my sister met
because of your actions.

60
00:06:46,458 --> 00:06:50,041
My sister was always
close with Luna,

61
00:06:50,125 --> 00:06:52,500
serving as her guardian.

62
00:07:03,416 --> 00:07:05,250
[BOOKS CLATTER]

63
00:07:19,750 --> 00:07:21,750
[SHATTERING SOUND]

64
00:07:21,833 --> 00:07:23,375
[LIZA YELLS]

65
00:07:24,333 --> 00:07:25,875
[LIZA GASPS]

66
00:07:48,666 --> 00:07:50,333
Luna...

67
00:07:50,416 --> 00:07:52,083
[CRACKING]

68
00:07:53,666 --> 00:07:56,916
[LYUZE] And that...
was just the beginning.

69
00:08:01,791 --> 00:08:03,041
[LYUZE] Hey sis.

70
00:08:03,125 --> 00:08:05,625
Does it feel
any better outside?

71
00:08:10,583 --> 00:08:12,083
[LYUZE GASPS]

72
00:08:17,833 --> 00:08:19,458
[CLATTERING]

73
00:08:28,625 --> 00:08:30,375
Liza!

74
00:08:34,041 --> 00:08:36,291
[CRACKING]

75
00:08:36,375 --> 00:08:41,333
[LYUZE] After Luna's
death... the ruin began.

76
00:08:41,416 --> 00:08:43,333
My sister was
the first victim...

77
00:08:43,416 --> 00:08:45,541
...and it's only
gotten worse.

78
00:08:47,666 --> 00:08:51,041
It's for those reasons
that I hate you to the core.

79
00:08:51,125 --> 00:08:56,500
Because of you and only you...
my sister is dead.

80
00:08:56,583 --> 00:08:59,375
You know she hated you too.

81
00:09:01,208 --> 00:09:05,375
Until her last moments...
she detested you.

82
00:09:10,958 --> 00:09:12,166
[LIZA] Casshern...

83
00:09:12,250 --> 00:09:14,666
[LYUZE] Liza.

84
00:09:14,750 --> 00:09:17,000
He is a calamity...

85
00:09:17,083 --> 00:09:19,208
A true
bringer of death...

86
00:09:19,291 --> 00:09:20,791
Please sister...

87
00:09:20,875 --> 00:09:22,583
Make sure
that Casshern...

88
00:09:22,666 --> 00:09:24,041
[CRACKING]

89
00:09:25,833 --> 00:09:29,166
[LYUZE] Those were
her last words.

90
00:09:29,250 --> 00:09:33,958
From that moment... I swore
I would avenge her death.

91
00:09:34,041 --> 00:09:37,208
By killing you with
my own two hands!

92
00:09:42,666 --> 00:09:44,208
[CASSHERN]
Tell me something.

93
00:09:44,291 --> 00:09:46,916
Just who was... Luna?

94
00:09:52,166 --> 00:09:56,375
Luna... was the source
of life in this world.

95
00:09:56,458 --> 00:10:00,166
A light of hope that shone
upon every living thing.

96
00:10:04,625 --> 00:10:09,583
And everyone is saying...
that I killed her.

97
00:10:15,333 --> 00:10:18,166
I understand...

98
00:10:18,250 --> 00:10:22,041
...exactly what I truly am.

99
00:10:22,125 --> 00:10:24,083
Just like your sister said,

100
00:10:24,166 --> 00:10:26,708
I bring calamity
to the world...

101
00:10:26,791 --> 00:10:29,500
And for that I don't
deserve to live.

102
00:10:29,583 --> 00:10:31,625
[LYUZE GASPS]

103
00:10:31,708 --> 00:10:35,833
[CASSHERN] If killing me
will fulfill your vengeance...

104
00:10:35,916 --> 00:10:39,458
No, not only that...
If my death will allow

105
00:10:39,541 --> 00:10:44,416
atonement for bringing ruin
and suffering to this world,

106
00:10:44,500 --> 00:10:47,000
then do with me as you wish.

107
00:10:49,291 --> 00:10:50,833
[CASSHERN]
If I am allowed to live,

108
00:10:50,916 --> 00:10:53,291
the only thing to come
of it will be more misery.

109
00:10:53,375 --> 00:10:54,708
[LYUZE THINKING] What?

110
00:10:54,791 --> 00:10:57,083
[CASSHERN] More lives will
be ended with these hands.

111
00:10:57,166 --> 00:10:58,291
[LYUZE THINKING]
What is he?

112
00:10:58,375 --> 00:11:01,125
[CASSHERN]
I must be stopped.

113
00:11:01,208 --> 00:11:02,833
Just do it.

114
00:11:08,541 --> 00:11:11,958
[LYUZE THINKING] What's wrong
with me? Why am I hesitating?

115
00:11:13,916 --> 00:11:15,250
[LYUZE THINKING]
Liza!

116
00:11:15,333 --> 00:11:16,541
[SHATTERING]

117
00:11:16,625 --> 00:11:19,208
[LYUZE GASPS]

118
00:11:19,291 --> 00:11:21,333
Die Casshern!

119
00:11:37,375 --> 00:11:41,458
It will take more than that...
to end my existence.

120
00:11:45,208 --> 00:11:48,500
Finish me off, do it quickly!

121
00:11:48,583 --> 00:11:50,416
Why are you standing there?

122
00:11:50,500 --> 00:11:51,916
Hurry!

123
00:11:54,666 --> 00:11:56,500
Take my life.

124
00:12:00,500 --> 00:12:03,875
[CASSHERN YELLS IN PAIN]

125
00:12:03,958 --> 00:12:06,083
You waited too long!

126
00:12:08,125 --> 00:12:10,583
Now hurry up and kill me!

127
00:12:16,291 --> 00:12:17,583
[FRIENDER SNARLS]

128
00:12:23,125 --> 00:12:23,958
[LYUZE YELLS]

129
00:12:24,041 --> 00:12:25,500
[CASSHERN GROANS]

130
00:12:28,250 --> 00:12:31,166
[LYUZE THINKING]
Why is he making that face?

131
00:12:31,250 --> 00:12:33,833
[LYUZE YELLS]

132
00:12:33,916 --> 00:12:35,416
[CASSHERN GROANS]

133
00:12:35,500 --> 00:12:38,125
[LYUZE] If you're a robot you
shouldn't be able to feel pain!

134
00:12:38,208 --> 00:12:41,041
Does that mean you're human?

135
00:12:41,125 --> 00:12:43,791
[CASSHERN]
I don't know.

136
00:12:43,875 --> 00:12:47,625
I don't know if I'm
a human or a robot

137
00:12:47,708 --> 00:12:50,458
Or if I'm something
else entirely.

138
00:12:51,625 --> 00:12:53,083
Something else entirely...?

139
00:12:53,166 --> 00:12:55,125
Then what are you?

140
00:13:04,083 --> 00:13:07,166
You cannot be allowed
to live any longer...

141
00:13:07,250 --> 00:13:08,833
For my sister...

142
00:13:08,916 --> 00:13:11,583
For Luna...

143
00:13:11,666 --> 00:13:13,583
For the world!

144
00:13:19,500 --> 00:13:21,208
[LYUZE GASPS]

145
00:13:21,291 --> 00:13:22,583
[LYUZE GROANS]

146
00:13:22,666 --> 00:13:24,375
[LYUZE YELLS]

147
00:13:37,583 --> 00:13:40,791
[LYUZE THINKING] Oh no...
I don't stand a chance.

148
00:13:42,791 --> 00:13:45,583
[LYUZE THINKING]
Liza... I'm sorry.

149
00:13:49,041 --> 00:13:50,833
Beautiful...

150
00:13:54,291 --> 00:13:57,500
[WHOOSHING]

151
00:13:57,583 --> 00:13:59,208
[EXPLOSION]

152
00:14:08,541 --> 00:14:09,708
[LYUZE GASPS]

153
00:14:26,208 --> 00:14:28,500
What am I...?

154
00:14:35,041 --> 00:14:38,958
[CASSHERN GROANS]

155
00:14:48,125 --> 00:14:53,000
[LYUZE SOBS]

156
00:15:13,625 --> 00:15:16,916
[FOOTSTEPS]

157
00:15:17,000 --> 00:15:19,416
Look everyone! I found it!

158
00:15:19,500 --> 00:15:22,458
[ROBOTS GASP]

159
00:15:22,541 --> 00:15:24,250
Here it is!

160
00:15:24,333 --> 00:15:29,291
[EXCITED CHATTER]

161
00:15:37,208 --> 00:15:38,791
It's just as I had hoped...

162
00:15:38,875 --> 00:15:42,875
The spare parts here
have yet to be ruined.

163
00:15:42,958 --> 00:15:44,666
Lucky for us none
of them have been

164
00:15:44,750 --> 00:15:46,708
stolen by bandits quite yet...

165
00:15:46,791 --> 00:15:49,541
There's still plenty of them
lying around back there.

166
00:15:49,625 --> 00:15:52,750
I might finally be able to
replace my damaged hand.

167
00:15:52,833 --> 00:15:55,250
This should give us
a few more months of life.

168
00:15:55,333 --> 00:15:57,375
How could we
ever repay you?

169
00:15:57,458 --> 00:15:58,583
You can start by helping me

170
00:15:58,666 --> 00:16:01,208
pick up these parts
as quickly as we can...

171
00:16:01,291 --> 00:16:04,208
If any bandits get
a whiff we'll be in trouble.

172
00:16:04,291 --> 00:16:05,666
[ROBOTS MURMUR]

173
00:16:05,750 --> 00:16:09,000
[ROBOT J] I do hope there's
a new set of legs for me.

174
00:16:10,416 --> 00:16:12,166
I'm so happy for them.

175
00:16:12,250 --> 00:16:14,125
[OHJI] Mm-Hmm...

176
00:16:15,833 --> 00:16:17,208
Here.

177
00:16:17,291 --> 00:16:19,541
Good work
finding this spot...

178
00:16:19,625 --> 00:16:21,666
Even though
the ruin is upon us,

179
00:16:21,750 --> 00:16:24,416
at least
everyone's still alive.

180
00:16:24,500 --> 00:16:26,708
If we can fit their
bodies with new parts,

181
00:16:26,791 --> 00:16:29,541
perhaps that will give them
some more hope for survival.

182
00:16:29,625 --> 00:16:32,625
Well I think it's always
better to be shiny than not!

183
00:16:32,708 --> 00:16:35,416
Heh, heh...
Guess you've got a point.

184
00:16:35,500 --> 00:16:38,166
Now then, why don't you go in
there and help the others?

185
00:16:38,250 --> 00:16:42,083
Sure... I'll see if I can find
something special for you!

186
00:16:42,166 --> 00:16:44,000
[RINGO GIGGLES]

187
00:16:44,083 --> 00:16:45,333
[THUD]

188
00:16:45,416 --> 00:16:46,541
[RINGO GASPS]

189
00:16:46,625 --> 00:16:48,625
[ROBOT BANDIT 1]
I smell something divine...

190
00:16:48,708 --> 00:16:52,000
Yes, the scent of
high-quality parts.

191
00:16:52,083 --> 00:16:54,125
Ringo get out of there!

192
00:16:54,208 --> 00:16:56,833
[WORRIED CHATTER]

193
00:16:56,916 --> 00:16:58,625
[ROBOT BANDIT 2] Good call
following  these twerps!

194
00:16:58,708 --> 00:17:00,541
They've led us
right to it! Ha! Ha!

195
00:17:00,625 --> 00:17:01,208
Ringo!

196
00:17:01,291 --> 00:17:02,625
[THUD]

197
00:17:04,083 --> 00:17:05,791
Ohji...!

198
00:17:05,875 --> 00:17:08,000
[ROBOT BANDIT 4]
I'd behave if I were you.

199
00:17:08,083 --> 00:17:12,666
[WORRIED CHATTER]

200
00:17:12,750 --> 00:17:14,375
No don't!

201
00:17:15,083 --> 00:17:17,750
[ROBOT L] There's tons
more just like this one!

202
00:17:17,833 --> 00:17:19,541
Ah...!

203
00:17:19,625 --> 00:17:21,041
[ROBOT BANDIT 1]
That's high-grade.

204
00:17:21,125 --> 00:17:23,541
Thanks a lot, kid.

205
00:17:23,625 --> 00:17:26,000
[WORRIED CHATTER]

206
00:17:26,750 --> 00:17:28,333
[CLATTERING]

207
00:17:28,416 --> 00:17:30,375
[ROBOTS GASP]

208
00:17:30,458 --> 00:17:32,208
[ROBOT M] Oh my!

209
00:17:39,375 --> 00:17:42,416
Go on get out of here Ringo!

210
00:17:42,500 --> 00:17:44,125
[THUD]

211
00:17:44,208 --> 00:17:46,541
[RINGO GASPS]

212
00:17:46,625 --> 00:17:48,833
Get your hands off of her!

213
00:17:50,666 --> 00:17:51,916
[ROBOT BANDIT 4]
You seem to know more about

214
00:17:52,000 --> 00:17:53,916
repair than the average bot...

215
00:17:54,000 --> 00:17:56,625
You'll be working for us now.

216
00:17:56,708 --> 00:17:58,375
[ROBOT BANDIT 6]
And if you refuse we'll use this

217
00:17:58,458 --> 00:18:00,541
little brat for spare parts...

218
00:18:00,625 --> 00:18:02,458
Or maybe we'll smash
her into a wall 

219
00:18:02,541 --> 00:18:05,875
and watch her explode
into a thousand pieces!

220
00:18:05,958 --> 00:18:07,458
No!

221
00:18:07,541 --> 00:18:08,750
[LOUD CRASH]

222
00:18:14,250 --> 00:18:15,375
[RINGO GASPS]

223
00:18:15,458 --> 00:18:17,041
Casshern!

224
00:18:20,250 --> 00:18:22,208
[ROBOT BANDIT 6] The bastard
who ripped off my arm...

225
00:18:22,291 --> 00:18:23,708
...was Casshern?!

226
00:18:25,625 --> 00:18:27,166
[ROBOT BANDIT 7]
Casshern?

227
00:18:27,250 --> 00:18:30,416
[ROBOT BANDIT 8] Looks like we
just walked into a gold mine.

228
00:18:30,500 --> 00:18:31,666
[ROBOT BANDIT 4]
If we eat him,

229
00:18:31,750 --> 00:18:33,625
we won't have to worry
about being ruined.

230
00:18:33,708 --> 00:18:35,083
[ROBOT BANDIT 4 LAUGHS]

231
00:18:36,208 --> 00:18:37,625
[ROBOT BANDIT 9]
The Casshern, huh?

232
00:18:37,708 --> 00:18:40,916
Well we don't need this
kid anymore now do we?

233
00:18:41,000 --> 00:18:43,291
No don't!

234
00:18:43,375 --> 00:18:44,458
[CRACK]

235
00:18:45,333 --> 00:18:47,166
[CRASHING SOUND]

236
00:18:49,250 --> 00:18:50,666
[CRUNCHING SOUND]

237
00:18:57,083 --> 00:19:00,541
[ROBOT BANDIT 10 YELLS]

238
00:19:03,708 --> 00:19:05,041
[ROBOT BANDIT 10 SCREAMS]

239
00:19:07,250 --> 00:19:09,708
[ROBOT BANDIT 1 SCREAMS]

240
00:19:09,791 --> 00:19:11,250
[ROBOT BANDIT 6]
Let's eat him!

241
00:19:11,333 --> 00:19:12,958
[ROBOT BANDIT 6 YELLS]

242
00:19:17,333 --> 00:19:18,958
[ELECTRIC BUZZING]

243
00:19:19,041 --> 00:19:21,666
[ROBOT BANDIT 6 SCREAMS]

244
00:19:37,125 --> 00:19:39,000
[ROBOT BANDIT 5 YELLS]

245
00:19:39,750 --> 00:19:42,083
[ROBOT BANDIT 11] Die!

246
00:19:44,958 --> 00:19:46,958
[ROBOT BANDIT 11 SCREAMS]

247
00:19:57,250 --> 00:19:59,041
[CASSHERN GRUNTS]

248
00:19:59,125 --> 00:20:03,708
[CASSHERN YELLS]

249
00:20:03,791 --> 00:20:05,708
Stop!

250
00:20:05,791 --> 00:20:07,583
[CASSHERN GASPS]

251
00:20:23,208 --> 00:20:25,166
[CASSHERN]
What have... I done?

252
00:20:25,250 --> 00:20:27,250
Casshern...

253
00:20:30,583 --> 00:20:35,000
You don't possess the
willpower to limit yourself.

254
00:20:35,083 --> 00:20:36,666
When you're fighting...

255
00:20:36,750 --> 00:20:40,333
...you don't stop til everything
around you's destroyed.

256
00:20:46,416 --> 00:20:50,125
[OHJI] In your blind rage you
almost killed both of us.

257
00:20:51,541 --> 00:20:55,708
[CASSHERN] Maybe... But I
did it in order to save you.

258
